metadata.name: Unrevealed Rolling Dino
metadata.description: Welcome to a collection of 6900 Rolling Dinos NFTs - unique non-fungible tokens living on the Etherium blockchain. Dinosaurs are extinct, but they keep on rolling. Each rolling dino is programmatically generated from over 100 possible traits, including rolling objects, headwear, facial expressions, and more. Every rolling object comes with a unique utility from which every Dino holder can benefit - regardless of the rarity.
